data.description: Welcome to 6271 Paloma Dr!  Whether you need to travel East or head West/downtown, this home is conveniently located just a couple minutes from Trans Mtn. Road! Downstairs, the home features an open concept to the living room, beautiful kitchen and breakfast area with its separate dining area. You also have a 3/4 bathroom downstairs. Upstairs you have the 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The primary bedroom  gives you a nice balcony to overlook the backyard and North East mountains. So come on by and look for yourself!
